Author: Icanmakeyouhappy
Text: You can do it! I believe in you 🌿  Accountability helps. If you need to check in, feel free. Ive been stuck in a restrict and binge cycle. I’ve logged all my food for tomorrow, and have actually begun intermittent fasting (16-8) because fuck knows. I think I’ve gained weight, (might be water weight) from the constant swaying between “just don’t eat, so you don’t have to log anything” to “fuck I’m ravenous”. *sigh* but like you said - it’s a new week! Good luck to us all 😭
